Achievements.Name: Railway Kingdom
Achievements.Description: Total railway assets exceed the total of non-railway assets by over 15% when the game is cleared.

Achievements.Name: Railway Microstate
Achievements.Description: Total rail length is less than 300 when the game is cleared.

Achievements.Name: Harmony With Nature
Achievements.Description: Blocks of trees exceed 300 when the game is cleared.

Achievements.Name: Tube Expansion
Achievements.Description: Total length of rails in tunnels exceeds 100.

Achievements.Name: City Expansion
Achievements.Description: Number of other companies' properties exceeds 1,000.

Achievements.Name: Bullet Train in Service
Achievements.Description: Complete the bullet train project to open a bullet train line.

Achievements.Name: Maglev Train in Service
Achievements.Description: Complete the linear train project to open a maglev train line.
